  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江社团一档写作类社刊，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://st.hujiang.com/mag/135231930/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em; border-right-width: 0px; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-left-width: 0px; margin-right: 5px;\" /></a>去沪江社团订阅本社刊！</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 28px; font-size: 15px;\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201601/7214dc3a-1216-4a41-ad87-5df3f55c479b.jpg\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 258px;\" /> </span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tWriting: imagine a scenario or express your opinion<br />\n\t<a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/Optimal\" target=\"_blank\">Optimal</a><br />\n\tOptimal means the most advantageous setting, taking into account most factors. What is optimal? How is it optimal?<br />\n\tThis week's topic: They searched for the optimal setting... (90-110 words)</p>\n<p>\n\tSuggestions:<br />\n\t1) optimal heat setting<br />\n\t2) optimal design<br />\n\t3) optimal performance</p>\n<p>\n\t4) calculating the optimal point<br />\n\t5) Instead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tOn the desk, there was no optimal location for a surveillance bug. The best location would probably be at the base of the desk lamp, with a view of the surface of the desk and the person sitting at the desk. There was no computer sitting on the desk, but the designer just assumed that there would be a laptop or tablet in the desk drawer or in the club manager's bag. Another location would probably be inside the receiver of the telephone, however, the designer doubted the usefulness of that.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166944827496/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768168/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p768168\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768859/\">摄影 世界各地女孩去上学 中国朴实伊朗高冷</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768976/\">《女医明妃传》大结局！医疗美剧补起来！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768455/\">《疯狂动物城》里动物的英文表达你知道嘛？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768470/\">FM热点速递：跟疯狂动物城学英文</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768591/\">10种未来最需要的工作，看看你适合什么？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p767988/\">BBC模仿秀: 穿帮音效</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768596/\">英文这么写，会冒犯女性的喂！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768380/\">6个励志小故事 快乐就是这么简单(2)</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768968/\">当迪士尼公主穿越回文艺复兴时期：好美腻！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p768644/\">巧手妈妈为女儿花样编发：这不是发型是艺术</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
